{"id":1691292,"retrievedAt":"2026-05-10T12:11:45.134Z","response":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[{"id":99,"name":"Documentary"}],"homepage":"https://howardcrowhurst.com/megaliths-forgotten-world/","id":1691292,"imdb_id":null,"origin_country":["FR"],"original_language":"en","original_title":"Megaliths, Forgotten World","overview":"Thousands of years ago, before the Romans, before the Greeks, even before the Old Kingdom of Egypt, an unknown people erected megalithic monuments on Earth.  Their works span continents and millennia, leading us to believe that they were distinct, unrelated populations.  But the similarity of the techniques used, the architectural principles and the engravings and sculptures indicate a common thought. It’s by examining the astronomical alignments, the geometry and the measurements of these monuments that we can be sure that they are all part of the same culture.","popularity":0.0071,"poster_path":null,"production_companies":[],"production_countries":[{"iso_3166_1":"FR","name":"France"}],"release_date":"2024-05-05","revenue":0,"runtime":94,"softcore":false,"spoken_languages":[],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"Megaliths, Forgotten World","video":false,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0,"alternative_titles":{"titles":[{"iso_3166_1":"FR","title":"Mégalithes, un Monde Oublié","type":""}]},"credits":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":6200942,"known_for_department":"Directing","name":"Howard Crowhurst","original_name":"Howard Crowhurst","popularity":0,"profile_path":null,"cast_id":5,"character":"voice-over","credit_id":"69ff19a3337a365b871e091e","order":0}],"crew":[{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":6200942,"known_for_department":"Directing","name":"Howard Crowhurst","original_name":"Howard Crowhurst","popularity":0,"profile_path":null,"credit_id":"69ff185a39a5ef9d40316d90","department":"Directing","job":"Director"},{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":4152987,"known_for_department":"Sound",